---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Jonathan Diaz" sideBarActiveItemID="about">
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">About Me</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
    <p class="text-lg">
      When I'm not working on image processing and tracking systems, I love getting out and exploring.
    </p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Florida Springs</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/90">
        I'm a big fan of traveling and exploring Florida's natural springs. We've been to
        Wekiva, Silver, Blue, De Leon, and several others around central Florida. There's
        something special about swimming in crystal-clear water and seeing the underwater
        world—it never gets old.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Food</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/90">
        I enjoy eating all kinds of foods, from KBBQ to seafood boils and everything in
        between. Always down to try something new.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
